        "heading_size": "h3",
        "text": "<p>At LNGVTY LABS, we redefine peptide quality with verified purity, consistency, and precision. Through our longstanding partnership with an FDA-licensed California drug manufacturer, every peptide we provide is crafted using Liquid Phase Peptide Synthesis (LPPS), ensuring cleaner, more reliable results for your research.</p><p>We believe in full transparency. That’s why our independent Certificates of Analysis (COAs) show both purity and true peptide content, so you know exactly what you’re working with.</p>",
