        "full": false,
        "image_position": "second",
        "caption": "",
        "heading_text": "<strong>The COA Purity Scam</strong>",
        "heading_size": "h3",
        "text": "<p>A \"99% purity\" chart spike doesn’t reveal the full truth. It shows the molecular structure match, but doesn’t tell you how much actual peptide is in the vial. Fillers, salts, and contaminants can account for a significant portion, leaving you guessing about the quality of the product.</p>",
        "button_label": "Access catalog",
        "button_link": "shopify://collections/all-products",
        "desktop_layout": "left",
        "mobile_layout": "multimedia-collage",
        "padding_top": 30,
        "padding_bottom": 50,
        "padding_top_mobile": 20,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 20
      }
    },
    "multimedia_collage_bfDpBC": {
      "type": "multimedia-collage",
      "blocks": {
        "image_kAgezK": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/hf_20260406_044955_b758ecf5-ebc5-4e4f-96a5-9334432ae037.png"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "image_kAgezK"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "",
        "full": false,
        "image_position": "first",
        "caption": "",
        "heading_text": "<strong>Liquid Phase Peptide Synthesis (LPPS)</strong>",
        "heading_size": "h3",
        "text": "<p>While most peptides on the market use cheaper Solid Phase Peptide Synthesis (SPPS), we use LPPS. This method offers step-by-step purification, eliminating impurities and ensuring that the peptide you’re buying is as pure as possible. The result? Reliable, high-quality peptides you can trust.</p>",
        "button_label": "",
